{"name":"About New Properties","type":"loot","img":"icons/commodities/tech/blueprint.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>The new expanded weapon list introduces the following new properties:</p>\n<p><strong>Heft. </strong>When attacking with this weapon, you must hold it with both hands and roll the versatile damage die, if it has one. With the <em>Titan's Grip</em> feat, you can use it with only one hand and roll the normal damage die when doing so.</p>\n<p><strong>Large</strong>. You have disadvantage when attacking with weapons with this property. With the <em>Titan's Grip</em> feat, you have no disadvantage. You have proficiency in Large weapons if you have proficiency in Martial weapons.</p>\n<p><strong>Oversized.</strong> It is impossible to wield weapons with this property normally.</p>\n<p><strong>Long Loading.</strong> Weapons with this property requires one action to reload and one to fire.</p>\n<p>If a feature lets you ignore the loading property of crossbows or you have 24 or more Strength or Dexterity, then treat this weapon as having the <em>Loading</em> property instead. If you satisfy both conditions, then ignore this property entirely.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attuned":false,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":2,"MaKucXrV3MVDHIa7":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.xTvVYj6JQ3KcesLh"}},"_id":"MZGEEXmlEuZp8KSn"}
{"name":"Variant Rule: Extra Attack","type":"loot","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/weapon_08.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can attack twice, instead of once, whenever you take the Attack action on your turn.</p>\n<p>Alternatively, you can forgo your extra attack and use your weapons as if you had the <em>Titan's Grip</em> feat's first set of features.</p>\n<p>At 17th level, fighters can instead forgo two of their four attacks and also gain the benefit of the <em>Titan's Grip</em> feat's second set of feature.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attuned":false,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":2,"MaKucXrV3MVDHIa7":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PqtnbmknyDNuPl7d"}},"_id":"598vYRxQDbO8Cb5H"}
